Class MyStack<E>

java.lang.Object
implementations.MyStack<E>
Type Parameters:
E - the type of elements held in this stack
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable, Cloneable, StackADT<E>
public class MyStack<E> extends Object implements StackADT<E>, Cloneable, Serializable
ArrayList-based implementation of the Stack Abstract Data Type (ADT). Uses a dynamic array (MyArrayList) to store elements.
See Also:
